OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F417A1775229063
OL,3,CMan who tried to rob bank with pretend
OL,4,Cgun jailed
OL,6,FA 64-year-old man who attempted to rob
OL,7,Fa bank in Kent while claiming to be
OL,8,Farmed with a gun has been jailed.
OL,10,FGary Fishlock was given a two-year
OL,11,Fprison sentence at Canterbury Crown
OL,12,FCourt on Wednesday.
OL,14,FFishlock entered a bank in Westwood
OL,15,FCross, Broadstairs, earlier this year
OL,16,Fon January 29, when he threatened
OL,17,Fstaff and demanded money.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/7
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
