OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,418,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41702
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F417A1775229063
OL,3,CMan who tried to rob bank with pretend
OL,4,Cgun jailed
OL,6,FHowever, his plan was ultimately
OL,7,Ffoiled after workers were able to
OL,8,Fraise the alarm, with armed police
OL,9,Fofficers arresting Fishlock at the
OL,10,Fscene.
OL,12,FOn the day of the attempted burglary,
OL,13,Fa female member of staff was
OL,14,Fapproached by Fishlock, who handed her
OL,15,Fa note reading: "I have a gun, put the
OL,16,Fmoney in the bag."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/7
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,418,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41703
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F417A1775229063
OL,3,CMan who tried to rob bank with pretend
OL,4,Cgun jailed
OL,6,FShe believed the threat to be genuine
OL,7,Fand immediately alerted her
OL,8,Fcolleagues, later telling police that
OL,9,Fshe feared Fishlock was carrying a
OL,10,Ffirearm.
OL,12,FFishlock pointed the bag slightly
OL,13,Fabove knee height towards her, giving
OL,14,Fthe impression that something was
OL,15,Finside, she said.
OL,17,FHe began to make further verbal
OL,18,Fdemands, before staff retreated to
OL,19,Fsecure rooms at the back of the bank,
OL,20,Fallowing them to contact emergency
OL,21,Fservices.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/7
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,418,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41704
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F417A1775229063
OL,3,CMan who tried to rob bank with pretend
OL,4,Cgun jailed
OL,6,FFishlock stayed inside the bank for
OL,7,Faround one minute after the alarm was
OL,8,Fsounded. He then left and stood
OL,9,Foutside the entrance.
OL,11,FJust 15 minutes after the initial call
OL,12,Fwas made, firearms officers arrived on
OL,13,Fthe scene and arrested him.
OL,15,FSubscribe for free to our weekly
OL,16,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,17,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,18,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/7
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
