OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,418,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41705
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F417A1775229063
OL,3,CMan who tried to rob bank with pretend
OL,4,Cgun jailed
OL,6,FA search revealed that no weapon was
OL,7,Finside the bag which he had brought to
OL,8,Fthe bank.
OL,10,FFishlock was remanded in custody and
OL,11,Flater charged with attempted robbery
OL,12,Fand possession of an imitation firearm
OL,13,Fin a public place.
OL,15,FHe attended Margate Magistrates' Court
OL,16,Fthe next day and later pleaded guilty
OL,17,Fto both charges.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/7
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
