PN,41706
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F417A1775229063
OL,3,CMan who tried to rob bank with pretend
OL,4,Cgun jailed
OL,6,FDetective Constable Adam Pope
OL,7,Fdescribed the crime as a "frightening
OL,8,Fordeal for the staff involved, who had
OL,9,Fno way of knowing whether the threat
OL,10,Fwas real".
OL,12,FHe said: "Fishlock's behaviour was
OL,13,Freckless and intimidating, and this
OL,14,Fsentence reflects the seriousness of
OL,15,Fhis actions, as well as the emotional
OL,16,Fdamage he has caused to those
OL,17,Finvolved."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G6/7
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
